    dc:description "FIG. 3. — Alvania proditoris (Thiele, 1925) n. comb.: A-E, lectotype, height 2.75 mm, width 1.65 mm, South Africa, Valdivia Stn 101, depth unknown, ZMB/Moll. N° 64965: shell (A-C); detail of the first whorls (D, E); F, original labels; G, original drawing. Scale bars: D, E, 20 μm." ;
